ento de la\\NNeutropenia Crónica Severa\\N(NCS)","guid":"WRnX5KSACt49S_u4-k35rQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"- Administración crónica (largo plazo)","guid":"nbVCLOFIdLpE0KscmY6P-A","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"- Reduce incidencia y\\Nduración de complicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"- Fiebre","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"- Infecciones recurrentes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"63","text":"- Úlceras orofaríngeas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"61","text":"- Para formas congénitas, cíclicas o idiopáticas","guid":"kUg7gtlnT4-A62T6O0O31w","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"61","text":"- Requiere monitorización a largo plazo (riesgo SMD/LMA)","guid":"TL3wjuPmyU7Xpc1fEZzvcQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"30","text":"F. Manejo del Síndrome\\NHematopoyético por Radiación Aguda\\N(H-ARS)","guid":"j-fXaUDyb0oFx8E5PQtlcg","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"- Aumenta supervivencia post-exposición a radiación mielosupresora (>2 Gy)","guid":"V6e_-kyDtbK9crTzPr6LEA","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"- Administrar lo antes posible tras exposición","guid":"KCrmDqkSIyaK6uQpfp7KVg","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"30","text":"G. Otras Indicaciones\\NPotenciales o Menos Comunes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"- Neutropenia en Infección por VIH avanzada","guid":"ER8RPNI83k1Fk_2rCzi7Kg","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"- Mucositis/Estomatitis inducida por quimioterapia","guid":"ap2oxGatLiz_7bbmnLSC8A","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"- Disponibilidad de productos\\Noriginales y biosimilares","guid":"","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"- Filgrastim (Neupogen®)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"- Pegfilgrastim (Neulasta®)","guid":"01ncDbPpORht_zLqLANtVg","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"- Biosimilares (Nivestym®, Zarxio