UlQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"186","parent":"166","text":"C. Contraindicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"- Hipersensibilidad a filgrastim/pegfilgrastim o excipientes","guid":"WkzvA31VHDWVFT9Epr25rA","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"166","text":"D. Precauciones en\\NPoblaciones Específicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"- Enfermedad de células falciformes","guid":"RQFcvizr77RAzyV8U9C2Ow","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"- Pediatría","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"188","text":"- Embarazo y lactancia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"188","text":"- Osteoporosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"188","text":"- Donantes sanos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"188","text":"- Potencial efecto sobre células malignas","guid":"ZMKCH8BWHBqiWU4xZrnlNw","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"188","text":"- Interacciones: quimioterapia, 5-FU, litio","guid":"tRnW2UsAxHxaRbPhKxqijw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"0","text":"VI. Consideraciones Especiales\\Npara el Ajuste de Dosis","guid":"JVxg58xc9yXWLg6W8CB0IA","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"A. Ajuste según Edad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"- Pediátrica: ajuste por peso para pegfilgrastim <45kg","guid":"4yHlnbYg_ScyLTNfLKAI1g","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"- Geriátrica: sin ajuste específico, pero >65 años = factor de riesgo","guid":"JS90SKPVs-O-i7zOVpbBMQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"200","parent":"196","text":"B. Ajuste según Peso","guid":"","children":[{"id":"201","parent":"200","text":"- Filgrastim: dosis en mcg/kg (ajuste intrínseco)","guid":"Nis94-MeShwvncy-uhu-DQ","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"200","text":"- Pegfilgrastim: 6mg dosis fija (≥45kg) o ajuste por rangos (<45kg)","guid":"e-85OEqyHkJWpZVjkcJqhw","children":[]}]},{"id":"203","parent":"196","text":"C. Ajuste según\\NFunción Renal/Hepática","guid":"","chi